#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:905
#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:1341
msgid ""
"All the Edit menu commands are also available in the menu that opens when"
" right-clicking the Xsheet/Timeline cells."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:907
msgid "**To edit cells with the Cells menu commands:**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:911
msgid "Use the **Reverse** command to invert the order of the selected cells."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:913
msgid ""
"Use the **Swing** command to append the selected cells, at the end of the"
" selection, in a reversed order. The last cell of the selection will not "
"be repeated."
