#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:925
msgid ""
"Use the **Increase Step** command to increase the animation step of the "
"selected cells by one unit."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:927
msgid ""
"Use the **Decrease Step** command to decrease the animation step of the "
"selected cells by one unit; if a drawing is exposed in one cell only, it "
"will be preserved."
