#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:933
msgid ""
"Use the **Roll Up** command to shift the content of selected cells up, "
"with the top cell content replacing the bottom cell one."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:935
msgid ""
"Use the **Roll Down** to shift the content of selected cells down, with "
"the bottom cell content replacing the top cell one."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:937
msgid ""
"All the Cells menu commands are also available in the menu that opens "
"when right-clicking the Xsheet/Timeline cells."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:939
