#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:959
msgid ""
"**Ctrl-click** (PC) or **Cmd-click** (Mac) the horizontal strip available"
" on the top of the cells, and drag them to the new position, duplicating "
"them."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:961
msgid ""
"**Shift-click** the horizontal strip available on the top of the cells, "
"and drag them to the new position, inserting them if other content is "
"exposed in the destination cells."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:963
msgid ""
"**Alt-click** the horizontal strip available on the top of the cells, and"
" drag them to the new position, overwriting any other content previously "
"exposed in the destination cells."
msgstr ""

