#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:1447
msgid ""
"Copy the file ``export-toonz.lua``  available in ``OpenToonz "
"stuff\\config``  folder into the ``C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Third Wish "
"Software & Animation\\Magpie Pro\\Scripts\\Export``  folder."
